<mjml>
  <mj-include path="./head.mjml" />
  <mj-body mj-class="body">
    <mj-wrapper background-color="#F0F0F0">
      <mj-section />
      <mj-section css-class="section">
        <mj-column>
          <mj-text mj-class="headline"
            >Hey ${mentorFirstName}, ${menteeFirstName} ${menteeLastName} has
            applied to you on ReDI Connect!</mj-text
          >
          <mj-divider mj-class="divider-top" css-class="divider" />

          <mj-text mj-class="text" padding="0 0 20px 0"
            >Dear ${mentorFirstName},</mj-text
          >
          <mj-text mj-class="text paragraph" 
            >On ${matchRequestedOn}, ${menteeFirstName} has applied to you as a
            mentee via ReDI Connect. So far, their application to you is still
            pending.
          </mj-text>
          <mj-text mj-class="text paragraph" 
            >Thatâ€™s why we wanted to follow up whether you have received this
            application? Sometimes the email notification about an application
            can go to your spam folder.</mj-text
          >
          <mj-text mj-class="text paragraph" 
            >If you did see it and cannot mentor ${menteeFirstName} for some
            reason, we would still ask you to get in touch to let them know. You
            will find a 'Decline mentorship' button in your profile. Please make
            sure to send with it a little text explaining your decision, so that
            they can start looking for another mentor
          </mj-text>
          <mj-text mj-class="text paragraph" 
            >Please reach out if we can support you with anything!</mj-text
          >

          <mj-text mj-class="text">All the best,</mj-text>
          <mj-text mj-class="text">Your ReDI Career Support Team</mj-text>
        </mj-column>
      </mj-section>
      <mj-include path="./footer.career.support.team.mjml" />
      <mj-section />
    </mj-wrapper>
  </mj-body>
</mjml>
